item.dc:creator: @Typh Typh
item.description:

jar10010:

:mad: god im so mad ive posted this a million times i hope one day a mod reads it but i made a domain on no-ip and then i got a server source so when i try to log onto my domain while running my server it takes me to other peoples hybridscapes. so if anyone has any idea how to fix this please help ;D

You are supposed to double-click runserver in your source, then open moparscape, and just type in name and pass.(Make sure the ip is 127.0.0.1 or localhost) That should do it.
